<paragraph base="F45931018" id="IFRS16_BC73"><paranum>BC73</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="BC73"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P1955">The IASB decided that an entity should account for leases of right-of-use assets (ie subleases) in the same way as other leases. Accordingly, subleases are within the scope of <xref base="F47962222" href="IFRS16_TOC.dita#IFRS16_TOC0001" id="IFRS16_X0834">IFRS 16</xref> (see <xref base="F47962223" href="IFRS16_gBC232-BC236.dita#IFRS16_gBC232-BC236/IFRS16_gBC232-BC236_TI" id="IFRS16_X0835">paragraphs BC232&#x2013;BC236</xref>).</p></body></paragraph>